        </item>
        <item>
            <title>抖音接通公安打擊網絡暴力，禁濫用 AI 製圖侮辱他人、洩露他人私隱、周圍貼罵街評論</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/douyinchina/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=douyinchina</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/douyinchina/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 06:00:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交網絡]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[抖音]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239580</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>網絡欺凌、網絡騷擾問題，在資訊發達年代為不少人帶來困擾。在 AI 流行後有更多受害者被 AI 繪圖在網路上被公審。抖音宣佈與公安機關建立線索回饋機制，將涉嫌違法犯罪的網暴線索即時報送至公安機關依法打擊。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1239587 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024053174409-503x580.jpg" alt="" width="503" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024053174409-503x580.jpg 503w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024053174409.jpg 780w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 503px" /></p><p>中國抖音指今年至今處置 162 件網絡暴力事件，攔截超過 5,000 萬條評論，並警示近 70 萬名施暴者。他們將推出「一鍵防網暴」功能，用户啟用後，7 天內不會收到非選定人羣發送的私信、彈幕及評論。若用户在平台內受到不當言論的傷害而不知如何用法律保護自己，抖音提供由中國法律諮詢中心解答的法律諮詢服務。抖音 App 防網暴功能入口：我 → 右上角菜單 → 更多功能 → 安全中心 → 小安防網暴 → 維權指引頁面。</p><p>官方披露的四類典型違規行為包括：濫用 AI 技術對他人進行挖苦與侮辱、評論洩露他人私隱訊息、四處粘貼辱罵言論及頻繁公開辱罵。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239582" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ff80cef4cdcb4d4d9273-249x580.jpg" alt="" width="249" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ff80cef4cdcb4d4d9273-249x580.jpg 249w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ff80cef4cdcb4d4d9273.jpg 386w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 249px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239583" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8a0d7ba916f2431b82e3-290x580.jpg" alt="" width="290" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8a0d7ba916f2431b82e3-290x580.jpg 290w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8a0d7ba916f2431b82e3.jpg 451w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 290px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239584" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/c86355f08da548439a72-354x580.jpg" alt="" width="354" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/c86355f08da548439a72-354x580.jpg 354w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/c86355f08da548439a72.jpg 549w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 354px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239585" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6ed72c7812d34e209a14-336x580.jpg" alt="" width="336" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6ed72c7812d34e209a14-336x580.jpg 336w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6ed72c7812d34e209a14.jpg 521w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 336px" /></p><div class="mceTemp"></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/772/235.htm">IT 之家</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/microsoft-cocreator/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】小畫家也可 AI 生成圖片　無須 VPN 免費用 Microsoft Cocreator</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/23/tinamind/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】AI 中文總結外語網頁、YouTube 影片，免 VPN 免費 ChatGPT 網頁工具  </a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/23/superclue-sensechatv5/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中國 AI 擊敗 GPT-4 成榜首，多項能力評測表現最好</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/douyinchina/life-tech/social-network/">抖音接通公安打擊網絡暴力，禁濫用 AI 製圖侮辱他人、洩露他人私隱、周圍貼罵街評論</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
